*Activates the Entrance Animation when there is another
"Future Saga" Category ally on the team*
- {passiveImg:once}DEF 100%{passiveImg:up_g} for 4 turn(s)
- {passiveImg:once}Guards all attacks for 4 turn(s)
*Basic effect(s)*
- Ki +3 and ATK & DEF 100%{passiveImg:up_g}
- Receives an additional Ki +2 per Type Ki Sphere obtained
*When there is a "Realm of Gods" Category enemy*
- ATK & DEF 50%{passiveImg:up_g}
- Attacks are effective against all Types
*As the 1st attacker in a turn*
- DEF 150%{passiveImg:up_g}
- High chance of evading enemy's attack
*As the 2nd or 3rd attacker in a turn*
- ATK 100%{passiveImg:up_g}
- DEF 50%{passiveImg:up_g}
- Launches an additional attack that has a high chance of
becoming a Super Attack
*When attacking with 20 or more Ki*
- Launches an additional Super Attack
